{"tid":1931720,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"好想養貓貓 時隔4個月依然未養到","createTime":"2020-03-18T10:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T21:21:11.000Z","uid":3539,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"60a1b909dc61055b61877fe120a4144c3e3b0859","tid":1931720,"uid":3539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:02:29.000Z","msg":"想養貓貓好耐 呢個念頭上年1月已經有 上年12月都開過一個post 到而家都未養到...<br />\n搵左成年都搵唔到領養<br />\nD義工一係話我未夠25歲 一係就屋企太多野 (香港人個個屋企都咁上下啦 個個住幾千尺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n一係就話我學生 (大佬我有收入架....)<br />\n<br />\n最近諗緊好無買貓好 但又怕助長無良養殖場<br />\n領養一向係我最先考慮 其次先係買自家繁殖<br />\n但發現自家繁殖D友仔都好串 個個都唔覆PM既<br />\n<br />\n又想試下好似連登仔發動技能 出街執<br />\n但我個個星期都出街搵 根本好難遇到<br />\n我真係好想養貓貓 我一定會好錫佢地架 <br />\n<br />\n點解我咁有愛心就養唔到貓 教大果兩個黑心壞人就領養到咁多隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人可以教下我點做好⋯"},{"pid":"7045f185b09801f76dc4c5f80fb26907bd991efb","tid":1931720,"uid":27277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無試下愛協"},{"pid":"175ef534556574397229ca02c7f6b460dd6229dd","tid":1931720,"uid":24368,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"有fd喺愛護動物協會領養到 手續好簡單<br />\n或者你可以做下research搵貓舍買<br />\n有唔少breeder都有良心既 唔會要隻貓生完一胎又一胎"},{"pid":"b666a0c1e9f0af13bd444f38751cdbf2089841c2","tid":1931720,"uid":39526,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"我半年前都係咁<br />\n上連登發多幾次癲就有貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzMDeZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzMDeZC.jpg&h=4e9ceeea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da497de3013ec7d474f8755636560379ab5ee8ec","tid":1931720,"uid":39526,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10