:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"義工的確會揀人出領養<br />\n可能當自己仔女掛<br />\n<br />\n當初我無諗急住加貓<br />\n有同事問我仲養唔養，介紹左個義工比我<br />\n我都唔算好熱衷追佢，同佢講有人要比左人先<br />\n最後想領養一隻，佢強行比左兩隻我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（雖然我又無所謂）<br />\n由開始計都搞一兩個月，係要時間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個義工算正常，我去寄義家庭睇左一次貓<br />\nSend相比佢睇屋企環境/窗網<br />\n第二次見已經直接拎埋貓+家訪<br />\n檢查下我屋企有無危險位<br />\n（要我用索帶扎死無網但唔會開的窗）<br />\n有問職業，無問人工，無問屋租定買"},{"pid":"12e39b1ce5f55c907a43ffdf57599a4664034f0f","tid":1931720,"uid":310534,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"咪幫襯自家繁殖，好多仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ebadb2f98fae6a07e841a530e8c537cdefc999","tid":1931720,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b666a0c1e9f0af13bd444f38751cdbf2089841c2","tid":1931720,"uid":39526,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"我半年前都係咁<br />\n上連登發多幾次癲就有貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzMDeZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzMDeZC.jpg&h=4e9ceeea&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d025bed67e9f166a8472b978949c2f5c116ee1e5","tid":1931720,"uid":59563,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"da497de3013ec7d474f8755636560379ab5ee8ec","tid":1931720,"uid":39526,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"補多句先<br />\n貓義工死全家<br />\n多謝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"咁你自己做位好既貓義工，自資日日出街餵貓，出錢幫街貓絕育執貓，再幫佢哋搵埋好主銀未得囉其實，仲要確保一定搵到頭好人家喎🤔"},{"pid":"2e9491dbb0a74e414af36767d1983e43ad8c751b","tid":1931720